{"tid":708013,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[蘋果照妖鏡] 余香凝個樣做乜衰咗咁多???","createTime":"2018-06-19T04:48:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T13:49:29.000Z","uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ceb3b360684a90bda6c38440cf4df08aaca68fed","tid":708013,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T04:48:29.000Z","msg":"余香凝心形糭應節<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180618/large/18ec3p5e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180618%2Flarge%2F18ec3p5e.jpg&h=f34f8168&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■余香凝日前為應端午節，學習包糭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n余香凝和胞妹余潔瀅（Zoe）為今天端午節，日前特別找師傅學包糭，余香凝說：「包糭要有牙力、又要有實力。」Zoe跟師傅學習，幾個步驟後已大叫：「點解啲饀料跌晒出嚟嘅？」余香凝平時甚少入廚，只會煮即食麵，雖然包糭並不純熟，但也不忘發揮創意，自創心形糭，不過被妹妹取笑心形糭形狀似蝴蝶結。<br />\nZoe平常會下廚，煮意粉或煎牛扒等，最撚手煮瑞士雞翼，全由余媽媽教授，她大爆兩姊妹曾經差點把廚房燒掉：「我哋試過整杯麵，落咗凍水就放入微波爐，點知冇摵走錫紙，燒咗微波爐個頂。」余香凝自言學過烹飪，但沒有天份。<br />\n採訪：王連連<br />\n攝影：葉君海<br />\n場地提供：城寨風味  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180618/large/18ec3p6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180618%2Flarge%2F18ec3p6e.jpg&h=cac2bdad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■余香凝坦承烹飪沒天份，相反妹妹（中）跟師傅學得似模似樣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180618/large/18ec3p7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180618%2Flarge%2F18ec3p7e.jpg&h=ddb9a9ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Zoe（右）自爆與胞姊余香凝曾因叮杯麵，差點火燒廚房。<br />\n<br />\n兩姊妹都唔同晒樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4bbee90ef373b9b69c6e58beebb1959f9b2918","tid":708013,"uid":108016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T04:52:53.000Z","msg":"食避孕藥食得多？"},{"pid":"87276feffb6b7cd843070095aab82ba5e0b3a98c","tid":708013,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"9e4bbee90ef373b9b69c6e58beebb1959f9b2918","tid":708013,"uid":108016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T04:52:53.000Z","msg":"食避孕藥食得多？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T05:28:37.000Z","msg":"食避孕藥會食到變樣架咩???"},{"pid":"d2438d2987c703e3636f954e541715917846d132","tid":708013,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T06:01:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0283985ced35dc33d5182747a26d1fdb9a1b55a1","tid":708013,"uid":123317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T11:38:26.000Z","msg":"臭雞"},{"pid":"001ebbfafd7b0c5297b6101a2be59a7bd375311c","tid":708013,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0283985ced35dc33d5182747a26d1fdb9a1b55a1","tid":708013,"uid":123317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T11:38:26.000Z","msg":"臭雞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:04:24.000Z","msg":"完全唔撚同咗樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d1fc7669391e21618e5da254e5faee6cf75eefd","tid":708013,"uid":166749,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"9e4bbee90ef373b9b69c6e58beebb1959f9b2918","tid":708013,"uid":108016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T04:52:53.000Z","msg":"食避孕藥食得多？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T13:49:29.000Z","msg":"食避孕藥會靚架喎"}]}